{
  "stem": "3524.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of those pictures that I showed you indicate the-- I tried to catch the reaction of some of the people as they saw that, and looking at the bodies.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were horrified, I believe, genuinely horrified.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whether they were horrified at trying to find out that what they thought was true was true, or whether this was a total surprise, I wouldn't want to make that judgement.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no interaction between them at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was probably more after I'd left the service that I learned about that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a tendency to put it behind us and go on to what our next task was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I probably became more aware of the general condition that existed when we reached our next assignment in Kamm, Germany, where we treated displaced persons from several parts of Europe, particularly near the Czechoslovakian border.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were aware that a number of people were, toward the end of the war, were running around with diseases and were needing treatment.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Army thought that we ought to set up some sort of hospitalization facilities in this particular area, so we went into what was a pretty, little town of Kamm, Germany, relatively untouched by the ravages of war.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were able to take over-- actually, I think we had four hotels in the group.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was particularly aware of one where we set up our pharmacy in the lobby of the [NON-ENGLISH] Hotel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there we would take in patients who were wandering throughout the fields.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sometimes they were brought in by Red Cross, or-- I don't know who actually found them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they heard about our location there and brought them in.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
